<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=David_Clayton-Thomas&action=edit&section=3.php.html" title="Edit section: Sources">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Sources">Sources</span></h2>
<ul>
